timeline.bodyText:
@kaisun2000
As I demonstrated in the PR that you got the diff for this PR from, there's a way to do this in a much simpler manner. You do not have to call all setters when you create an instance of ZkClientConfig.
Could you please see https://github.com/apache/helix/pull/770/files#diff-74feb4babccc9de65b296f5a79178548R84 and revise this piece of code accordingly?

